text: László Hauler (26 June 1884 - 12 September 1914) was a Hungarian sports shooter. He competed in five events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1884 births Category:1914 deaths Category:Hungarian male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Hungary Category:Shooters at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:People from Satu Mare County
